param.query:
SELECT 
-- 날짜열 함수

   datetime('now') now_datetime
  , date('now') now_date
  , time('now') now_time
  , strftime('%s','now') now_strftime
  
  , strftime('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S', x5) datetime
  , strftime('%Y-%m-%d', x5) date
  , strftime('%Y', x5) yyyy
  , strftime('%m', x5) month
  , strftime('%d', x5) dd
  , strftime('%H', x5) hh
  , strftime('%M', x5) minute
  , strftime('%S', x5) ss
  , strftime('%w', x5) dayofWeek
  , strftime_ak(x5) strftime_ak
  , strftime_aak(x5) strftime_aak
  , strftime_a(x5) strftime_a
  , strftime_aa(x5) strftime_aa
  , strftime('%W', x5) weekofYear 
  
  , strftime('%Y-%m-%d','2019-01-17 12:39:29') strftime_ak1
  , strftime('%Y-%m-%d','2019-01-17T12:39:29') strftime_aak1 -- 중간에 T 붙여도 됨
  
  , date(x5,'-1 day') minus_1day
  , date(x5,'+1 day') plus_1day
  , date(x5,'-1 month') minus_1month
  , date(x5,'+1 month') plus_1month
  , date(x5,'-1 year') minus_1year
  , date(x5,'+1 year') plus_1year
  , date(x5,'start of month','+1 month','-1 day')  end_day-- last day of the month
  , date('now','start of month','+1 month','-1 day') now_end_day -- last day of the current month 
  
from #{DF(0)}

param.query:
SELECT a.cust_id 
	, a.rank		-- 고객별 매출액 순위
	, a.sum			-- 고객별 매출액
	, a.cum_sales	-- 누적매출액
	, a.tot_sales	-- 매출총액
	, round(a.sum/a.tot_sales*100, 4) rto 			-- 고객별 매출액 비중
	, round(a.cum_sales/a.tot_sales*100, 4) cum_rto -- 누적 매출액 비중
from (select a.cust_id
		  , rank() over (order by a.sum desc) rank
		  , sum 
		  , sum(a.sum) over (order by a.sum desc ) cum_sales
		  , sum(a.sum) over () tot_sales
	from #{DF(0)} a
	) a

param.query:
SELECT a.ctg_1
	, a.ctg_2 
	, a.rank		-- 중카테고리별 매출액 순위
	, a.sum			-- 중카테고리별 매출액
	, a.cum_sales	-- 누적 매출액
	, a.tot_sales	-- 매출총액
	, round(a.sum/a.tot_sales*100, 4) rto	 		-- 중카테고리별 매출액 비중
	, round(a.cum_sales/a.tot_sales*100, 4) cum_rto	-- 누적 매출액 비중
from (select a.ctg_1, a.ctg_2
		  , rank() over (partition by ctg_1 order by a.sum desc) rank
		  , sum 
		  , sum(a.sum) over (partition by ctg_1 order by a.sum desc ) cum_sales
		  , sum(a.sum) over (partition by ctg_1) tot_sales
	from #{DF(0)} a
	) a
order by a.ctg_1, a.rank
